latestIgtvVideos.title: Lakme Matte Moist Range 🧚🏻‍♀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Since I am always on the lookout for new products, I decided to try out the @lakmeindia Matte Moist Range. Needless to say I was impressed. The range encompasses a toner, moisturiser and a clay mask that promises to nourish your skin, whilst keeping it matte.

First up, Toner! I did feel a very light tingly, cool feeling but my skin appeared more refreshed. The product also tightened my pores and left it looking really matte, but not dry.

Clay mask : I have a thing for clay masks and this one checked all the boxes for me. My skin felt uber fresh, bright with visibly shrunk pores. 

PS: Unlike other clay masks, this one doesn’t dry out your skin! 

Moisturizer: As I started applying the moisturizer on my face and neck, I was quite taken by the light-weight formulation that melted into my skin and left no greasy residue behind. Perfect for the summer when our skin starts feeling oily! #AD

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dyson Corrale 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’ve had dry and frizzy hair for as long as I can remember. This meant that I’ve always depended on a straightener to style my hair. Over the years I’ve really damaged my hair due to high heat and poor quality straighteners. That’s made me really conscious of the styling tools I use on my hair. 

But all that’s going to change now because I’ve just got my hands on Dyson Corrale! I’m unequivocally in love with this baby right here. Say goodbye to heat damage because it styles your hair with 50% less heat damage and requires only 1-2 passes to get the required style. It’s suitable for all hair types and definitely works wonders for me. My hair feels shinier, smoother and healthier now. 

I style my hair very often so it’s nice to know that it can be fully charged in under 70 minutes. It’s also cordless meaning that i can effortlessly style my hair even when I’m on the go. It’s definitely the best straightener I’ve ever had and I hope you feel that way as well. If you don’t, there’s nothing to fret about since you can return it within 30 days for a 100% cash back!!! 
.
.
#GoodbyeExtremeHeat #Dyson #DysonCorrale
